dc_description_s: This raster dataset shows administrative districts in Hungary. The source of the map is the 1:10 000 scale, house number depth vector map file, the DSM-10 map,  which is made for all settlements of the country - their interior and exterior - in a uniform structure and data content. The data content of the DSM-10 map file has been constantly expanding since 1998, based on on-site surveys, state data sources and user feedback, so the data content of the GeoX Kft.raster map is constantly being updated. GeoX Kft. (2020). Districts, Hungary, 2022. GeoX Kft. Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/cy924xj3947 This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
